/i>  <i>G</i>\r\n</u><u>          <i>Am7</i>  <i>F</i>  <i>C9</i>  <i>G</i>\r\n</u><u>          <i>Am7</i>  <i>F</i>  <i>C9</i>  <i>G</i>\r\n</u><u>          <i>Am7</i>  <i>F</i>  <i>C9</i>  <i>G</i>\r\n\r\n</u><u>Parte 1 de 2\r\n\r\n</u><b>E|----------------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>B|-13-13-13-12-12-8-8-8-13-13-13-12-12-8-8------------|\r\n</b><b>G|----------------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>D|----------------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>A|----------------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>E|----------------------------------------------------|\r\n\r\n</b><u>Parte 2 de 2\r\n\r\n</u><b>E|----------------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>B|------------------8---------------------8-----------|\r\n</b><b>G|----7-9--7-9--7-9---9-----7-9--7-9--7-9---9---------|\r\n</b><b>D|-10--------------------10-------------------10------|\r\n</b><b>A|----------------------------------------------------|\r\n</b><b>E|----------------------------------------------------|\r\n\r\n</b><u>[Ponte]\r\n\r\n</u><u><i>D9</i>            <i>Am7</i>\r\n</u><u>  Maravilhado, extasiado\r\n</u><u><i>C9</i>                      <i>G</i>\r\n</u><u>  Eu fico ao ouvir Teu nome\r\n</u><u><i>D9</i>\r\n</u><u>  Jesus, Teu nome é força\r\n</u><u><i>Am7</i>\r\n</u><u>  É fôlego de vida\r\n</u><u><i>C9</i>                 <i>G</i>\r\n</u><u>  Misteriosa água viva\r\n\r\n</u><u>[Refrão]\r\n\r\n</u><u><i>D9</i>\r\n</u><u>  Santo, Santo, Santo\r\n</u><u><i>Am7</i>\r\n</u><u>  Deus Todo Poderoso\r\n</u><u><i>C9</i>                       <i>G</i>\r\n</u><u>  Que era, e é, e há de vir\r\n</u><u><i>D9</i>\r\n</u><u>  Com a criação eu canto\r\n</u><u><i>Am7</i>\r\n</u><u>  Louvores ao Rei dos reis\r\n</u><u><i>C9</i>\r\n</u><u>  És tudo para mim\r\n</u><u>  <i>G</i>           <i>D9</i>\r\n</u><u>E eu Te adorarei</u>"
